    "navbar": "",
    "text": "Affordable, practical luxury.\nCall Now\nNew! Tint Simulator\nCutting Edge Window Tinting\nTint shop located in Watauga, Texas.\nOver 10 years of experience in Window Tinting in the Dallas-Fort Worth area.\naboutus\nCutting Edge Window Tinting is a family owned and operated business in Watauga, Texas, specializing in Automotive Window Tinting. \n  Cutting Edge is located in the DFW area allowing us access to Watauga, Bedford, Hurst, Fort Worth, Keller, Haltom City and beyond. \n  We lead with integrity and take pride in the quality of our film and services, offering a lifetime guarantee on all window tint installations. We know you'll have a positive experience from the first point of contact to when you get your car home. \n  Our professionalism, integrity, and customer service is what sets us apart from the rest. \n  You'll find our new location just off of Watauga Road/Western Center and 377/Denton Hwy. on 5930 Plum Street, Suite 136.\n  Don't forget to check out our five star rating on Google! \nCONTACT\nUS\nTel. 817-542-6673\nInstagram\nFacebook\nVISIT\nUS\nMonday - Friday 10:00 - 6:00\nSaturday 9:00 - 4:00\n5930 Plum Street STE. 136\nWatauga, TX 76148\n TELL\nUS\nSubmit\nWHAT PEOPLE SAY\nCOLE SHERIFF\nJake replaced the eyebrow on my pickup. He and his wife were both very polite and professional. Pricing and timeliness were both impeccable. He was even nice enough to clean up my windows (even the ones he didn't tint). I highly recommend these folks.\nCARL SNOW\nMy first time using Jake and Cutting Edge Window Tinting and they did an excellent job! He was fast, professional, and tinted my windows at a great price! I have used several other companies in the past, including high-end companies in both Dallas and Fort Worth, and this job was equal or better than any tinting service I have used before. I highly recommend Cutting Edge Window Tinting, especially if you want to support a hard working, local small business.\nJON SACIA\nJake at Cutting Edge Window Tinting in Ft. Worth did an outstanding job on my wife’s car. Very good pricing and did great work in the time that was told to us. We will definitely be using this company going forward!\n\nThank you!\nSocial Media \nAngelene Story\nOct 21\n1 min\nQ & A: Have you ever asked yourself one of these when thinking about getting your windows tinted?\nWhat are the different tint percentages? At Cutting Edge, we offer three tiers of film and the brand we carry is Global Film. We offer a...\n3 views\n0 comments\n1 like. Post not marked as liked\n1\nAngelene Story\nOct 21\n3 min\nDon't DIY your tint job\nHigh-quality window film is distributed by reputable companies throughout the country. The film produced by these established companies...\n1 view\n0 comments\n2 likes. Post not marked as liked\n2\nOur Blog\nCutting Edge Window Tinting\nCall (817) 542-6673 to book now!\n©2023 by Cutting Edge Window Tinting.\nPrivacy Policy & Terms and Conditions\nCurrently servicing Watauga, Saginaw, Keller, Fort Worth, North Richland Hills, Richland Hills, Roanoke, South Lake, Hurst, Colleyville, Bedford and other surrounding areas.\nAccept\nCookie Settings\nWe use cookies and similar technologies to enable services and functionality on our site and to understand your interaction with our service. By clicking on accept, you agree to our use of such technologies for marketing and analytics.See Privacy Policy",
